title: Unknown / Blackout (2006) No Names. No Past. Survival’s A Deadly Puzzle.

sources.title: Unknown / Blackout (2006) No Names. No Past. Survival’s A Deadly Puzzle.
sources.description:
After waking up with amnesia in a locked warehouse, five men must, in order to stay alive, try to determine who among them is an ally and who is an enemy.

Original title: Unknown (2006)
Alternative titles: Identità sospette (Italian), Blackout (France), 5 неизвестных (Russian), Mentes en blanco (Spanish), Bilinmeyen (Turkish), Nieznani (Polish), 

Director: Simon Brand
Writer: Matthew Waynee

Main cast:
Jim Caviezel – Jean Jacket / Mitch Wozniak
Greg Kinnear – Broken Nose / Richard McCain
Barry Pepper – Rancher Shirt / William Coles Jr.
Joe Pantoliano – Bound Man / Brockman
Jeremy Sisto – Handcuffed Man / Bobby Kinkade
Bridget Moynahan – Eliza Coles
Peter Stormare – Snakeskin Boots / Stefan Burian

Genres: Mystery, Thriller, Crime, Drama, Giallo
Release date: November 3, 2006 (USA)
Filming location: Coachella Valley, California, USA
